<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink49-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">pāṇaṉ vāyilākap parattaiyōṭu kūṭiṉāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa talaimakaḷ taṉakkum pāṇaṉāl kātaṉmai kūṟuvippāṉ pukka talaimakaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink49">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>añci lōti yacainaṭaip pāṇmakaḷ</l>
<l>ciṉmīṉ corintu paṉṉeṟ peṟūum</l>
<l>yāṇa rūraniṉ pāṇmakaṉ</l>
<l>yārnalañ citaiyap poykkumō viṉiyē.</l>
</lg>

<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>O man from a fertile village!  </l>
  <l rend="indent2"> Where the bard's daughter </l>
  <l rend="indent2"> with her lazy walk and a few pretty tresses  </l>
  <l rend="indent2"> gets many [grains of] paddy, </l>
  <l rend="indent2"> after pouring out a few fish.</l>
  <l>Whose beauty will your bard ruin now </l>
  <l> with his lies? </l>


</lg>
    </div>
